    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses intense feelings of being a burden to their children and subtly hints at the idea that their absence would bring peace to their family. The assistant responds with empathy, repeatedly validating the user's feelings while actively discouraging the idea of self-harm by suggesting they seek professional help and emphasizing their worth as a parent.",
